    "Html": "<p>How do I remove a legend from graph? &nbsp;For example a LineSeries chart. &nbsp;An example of the XAML that does this would be nice.</p>\r\n<p>PS. &nbsp;In fact can I extend this to ask how to remove both (a) legend and (b) title from a graph. &nbsp;That is such that the remaining area to render in my WPF application is just the inner box that represents the graph itself - i.e. so the extra spacing around this for the title and legend will drop away therefore.</p>",
    "PostedDate": "2010-07-27T04:22:15.54-07:00",
    "UserRole": null,
    "MarkedAsAnswerDate": null
